\nw[Inn]Welcome to the inn. If you have any business,
please feel free to let us know.
Take a break (20G)
I don't have any particular business
\nw[Mistress]I don't have enough money.

\nw[Inn]Um... this side is a private room, so please don't
enter.
\nw[Bartender]Welcome, please make yourself comfortable.
\nw[Taro](Shall we have a meal...?)
Have a meal with Kuno?
Let's not
\nw[Kuno]That's fine, it looks like there are empty seats.
back_droom_001

\nw[Kuno]As expected, the meals at the largest tavern in
town are the best. The portions are generous.

\nw[Taro]Well, when it comes to adventurers, quantity is
important. And also strong flavors.
\nw[Taro](Well, what should we talk about?)
Since joining the mercenary group
About your preferred type
Things I want to do after getting married

\nw[Taro]How do you feel about joining the mercenary group
so far? I'm sure there have been various
experiences...

\nw[Kuno]It's true that there have been various
experiences, but the most important thing is that
I've definitely become stronger. I've become so
much stronger compared to when I was in Dios,
haven't I?

\nw[Kuno]Becoming a succubus was a big reason, but the main
reason I became stronger is because of my
equipment... It's complicated.
\nw[Taro]Ah, well, that's certainly true...

\nw[Kuno]Strong weapons are completely different. While
they may be heavier, they can easily cut through
monsters and are durable.

\nw[Kuno]Having sturdy armor makes a huge difference in
damage, you know. And since I also have magic
power, I'm strong against magic attacks too. Plus,
it helps reduce damage when I get attacked in
vulnerable spots.

\nw[Kuno]And also, the magic orbs, right? With those, I can
use magic, so I can become really strong in
battles, you know.

\nw[Kuno]Even though it's said that it takes several years
to become an apprentice to a magician and learn
magic...

\nw[Taro]Well, the truth is, becoming a succubus did make
me stronger, but it's just that I became strong
enough to use powerful weapons.

\nw[Taro]If my equipment were to become worse, I feel like
I would only become slightly stronger than when I
was in Dios.

\nw[Kuno]That's right. Equipment is consumable, so I have
to continuously earn money too.

\nw[Kuno]I'm glad I became a succubus. Being able to work
at this adult establishment and earn money from
men, as well as having the charm effect to be
favored by merchants and such.
\nw[Taro]I see... That's certainly true.

\nw[Taro]The trade of magic orbs and the trust in Prae are
what made it possible. If I hadn't joined this
mercenary group and come to this country, things
could have been really tough.
\nw[Kuno]Yes, that's why I'm thankful.

\nw[Taro]In terms of romantic preferences, what type does
Kuno like? I'm thinking of trying to make various
lovers.
\nw[Kuno]You're asking difficult questions, aren't you?

\nw[Taro]We've been living a tough life, haven't we? I
don't think we've really had the luxury to think
about romantic matters.

\nw[Taro]Originally, it's not like I wanted to marry Nonna
because I romantically liked her, especially
Nonna.

\nw[Kuno]......If it was before I had various experiences
here, I probably would have denied it, but now
that I think about it, yes.

\nw[Kuno]I just wanted a solid connection and form with the
important people in my life. Marriage happened to
be the means for that.
\nw[Taro]Yeah, that's right...

\nw[Kuno]Just because of that, it doesn't mean I wanted to
marry Taro and do various things as a married
couple!

\nw[Kuno]I definitely thought about things like having
children and all, and there's no doubt that I
romantically liked it too!
\nw[Taro]O-Okay...

\nw[Taro](I wonder which one of us made the first move
though)

\nw[Taro](Did I want to get married because I romantically
liked the other person, or did I want to get
married because I wanted to romantically like
them...)

\nw[Taro]Well, it's not like it matters either way, and I'm
sure even the person involved wouldn't know for
sure...

\nw[Kuno]Even if you say that, I don't know what my type
is. Ever since becoming an succubus, I easily fall
in love, you know.
\nw[Taro]Is that so?

\nw[Kuno]It's embarrassing to say, but honestly, anyone
would develop feelings if they were penetrated by
a penis.
\nw[Taro]Ah, the characteristics of my subordinate...

\nw[Kuno]If I can feel really good, even after sexual
intercourse, it leaves a good impression. And even
if it doesn't feel that great, having sex reduces
the negative impression.

\nw[Kuno]...Could it be that my preference is someone who
is good at sex?
\nw[Taro]...Maybe...
\nw[Kuno]......*sigh*...

\nw[Taro]Now that Prae's condition has stabilized, I've
been thinking about getting married. Do you have
any thoughts about married life?

\nw[Kuno]It would be nice if I, Nonna, and Taro could get
married, right?

\nw[Kuno]There are many things, but the first thing I want
to do is have relationships with lots of men!

\nw[Taro]Ah, I'm sorry. It's to fulfill my desire for being
cuckolded...

\nw[Kuno]Don't worry, at first it was just your desire, but
now it's different. I want to have connections
with various people.

\nw[Kuno]When I was with Dios, I was only interested in you
and Nonna. But I realized that it would only
burden the two of you.

\nw[Kuno]I want to get married and live supporting each
other with everyone. But I'm sorry, I can't live a
life where I rely on just the two of you.

\nw[Taro]Huh? Isn't it just about wanting to fulfill your
cuckold fetish?

\nw[Kuno]When I was searching for a treatment for Prae, I
realized that human connections are important,
right? It's called a network, isn't it?

\nw[Kuno]You wouldn't help someone you're not close with,
right? It's a good thing to become friends with
many people so that they can help you when you're
in trouble.

\nw[Kuno]When it comes to having romantic feelings for
someone, it's okay to be a little reckless. So I
think it's good to have many friends with benefits
or lovers.

\nw[Kuno]Besides, I'm currently a succubus, a mercenary,
and a sex worker. When I think about it, it's
actually normal for someone in my position to have
many lovers.

\nw[Taro]Ah, that's true. For mercenaries, it's better to
have physical relationships with many people of
the opposite sex to enhance their magical power.
It goes without saying for the rest.

\nw[Kuno]So when we get married, I'll have lots of romantic
relationships with other men to make you jealous
and want to cuckold me. Look forward to it.
\nw[Taro]... Hehe, I see. I'm looking forward to it.
Listen to Kuno's story

\nw[Kuno]It would be nice if we can relax now that we've
defeated the Earth Beast.

\nw[Taro]Yeah, I hope we won't have any more chances to
fight against something like that.

\nw[Kuno]Since we were able to defeat the Earth Beast,
can't we pretty much defeat most other monsters
too?

\nw[Taro]No, I heard it from Louis. The Earth Beast itself
may be strong, but the monsters inside its body
aren't really that strong.

\nw[Taro]Besides, well, it seems that the necessary skills
for dealing with monsters and humans are
completely different, so I guess I'll have to
learn those too...
\nw[Taro]Huh, what's wrong? Did I say something strange?

\nw[Kuno]...I've been thinking about it for a while, but
what do you think of Louis, Taro?
\nw[Taro]What's wrong?

\nw[Kuno]It seems like we get along pretty well, but do you
want to be my lover?
\nw[Taro]Huh? Me and Louis?
\nw[Kuno]Yeah.

\nw[Taro]That's not the case. As the leader, I have to know
various tasks, so I just receive a lot of
guidance.

\nw[Kuno]But you often say things like I heard it from
Louis or I asked Louis. You seem to trust the
information quite a bit.

\nw[Taro]No, because Louis may have a foul mouth, but he's
not the kind of person who would lie so much...
\nw[Kuno]You still trust him, don't you?
\nw[Taro]Is that so...?

\nw[Taro](Well, I did receive a lot of guidance from Louis
regarding work, so it's true that I rely on
him...?)
\nw[Taro](Well, even so...)

\nw[Taro]Well, I do think she's beautiful, but she doesn't
have the personality. She's probably not my type.
\nw[Kuno]Because she's not a married woman?

\nw[Taro]Just because I get sexually excited by married
women doesn't mean I like them in a romantic
sense, you know!?
\nw[Kuno]Hehe, I understand. I'll believe you this time.
\nw[Taro]If that's the case, then it's fine...

\nw[Taro](Is Kuno quite jealous? No, is it normal to be
this jealous?)
\nw[Taro](I don't know...)
\nw[Taro](Shall we have a meal...?)
Have a meal with Nonna?
Let's not
\nw[Nonna]Yes, I understand.
back_droom_001

\nw[Taro]The taste is different from the meals we have with
the group, it's more intense.

\nw[Nonna]During adventures, we often have bland meals. And
when you're physically active, you crave stronger
flavors.
\nw[Taro](Now, what should we talk about?)
About our current life
About marriage
About the dissatisfaction

\nw[Taro]What does Nonna think about the current life in
the mercenary group?

\nw[Nonna]I think it's a good life. Prae is kind, and while
there are some troublesome members, most of the
group members are good kids.

\nw[Taro]Is there anything you dislike about being in this
group? There are even brothels, and the
relationships with men are different from
before...

\nw[Nonna]It's certainly different from before, but it's not
a bad change.

\nw[Nonna]It's good that I can still work even when I'm
pregnant. Prae plays a big role in gaining trust
in this town.

\nw[Nonna]Well, I did originally plan to come to this
country, so it was lucky that I was picked up by
Prae, who has a solid foundation.

\nw[Taro]Well, yeah. Since I've become the leader of the
mercenary group, I have to work hard to earn the
trust of someone like Prae.
\nw[Nonna]Yes, I'm cheering for you.

\nw[Taro]What does Nonna think about marriage? Originally,
she wasn't enthusiastic about a marriage involving
three people, right?

\nw[Nonna]Well, I always thought that it would be best if
the two of us got married.

\nw[Nonna]Originally, we trusted each other and became a
family, so I thought we could become a good couple
even without strong romantic feelings.

\nw[Nonna]But now the situation has changed. Kuno's trauma
has become stronger, and we have also become
succubi and been caught up in Taro's sexual
preferences.
\nw[Taro]O-Okay...

\nw[Nonna]I'm not blaming you. As I said, the situation has
just changed.
\nw[Nonna]I have to reconsider my thoughts on marriage.

\nw[Nonna]I was considering marriage as the goal of love,
but when I think about Taro's NTR fetish, marriage
is not the end goal, but rather a process.

\nw[Nonna]Besides, in this country, marriage allows for
freedom in the number of people involved. So I
think we need to see marriage as one of the means.
\nw[Taro]One of the means...

\nw[Nonna]However, it's not something that can be switched
immediately. I intend to gradually change my
values.

\nw[Taro]Yeah, you're right. I also need to think seriously
as an incubus.

\nw[Taro](However, my sexual preference is probably
something that can't be changed easily. I have
this twisted fetish where I get excited when I'm
embraced by someone I don't want to be embraced
by...)

\nw[Taro]Since coming here, I haven't heard any complaints
from Nonna, but do you have any unspoken
grievances that you want to let out?

\nw[Taro]I may be seen as unreliable, but I am also the
leader, so if there's anything, I want you to tell
me.

\nw[Nonna]I had some complaints... well, not like they
didn't exist, but I'm not really concerned about
them now.

\nw[Taro]If there were any in the past, I want you to tell
me. I intend to continue living together with
Nonna in the future, and honestly, since coming
here, I haven't had much time to see Nonna, so I
haven't been able to pay much attention to her.
\nw[Nonna]Well... If Taro wants to know.

\nw[Nonna]At first, I had a disgust towards having physical
relationships. I also didn't have any experience
with men.
\nw[Taro]So, you didn't want to be embraced after all...

\nw[Nonna]But, as I said, I wanted to repay Prae. So even
though I didn't want to, I accepted it and tried
to get used to being with men.

\nw[Nonna]Now I've completely come to enjoy sexual
activities, and I no longer have any complaints.

\nw[Taro]I see... However, I didn't notice that Nonna was
reluctant...

\nw[Nonna]I was trying not to say it out loud. I also didn't
want to burden the two of you.
\nw[Taro]I'm sorry, I'm not reliable...

\nw[Nonna]It's because you two are like my children. You
don't need to worry about it.
Listen to Nonna's story

\nw[Nonna]Is Taro thinking about what to do with the
mercenary group from now on?

\nw[Taro]Ah, for now, we should focus on increasing the
number of members in the group.

\nw[Taro]If possible, I would like to increase the number
of mercenaries, but even if they're just regular
sex workers who can't fight, I still want to
increase their numbers.

\nw[Taro]We have a small number of members in our mercenary
group, so we can only take on small-scale
requests.

\nw[Nonna]Are you thinking about it properly? Or did Prae
tell you to say that?

\nw[Taro]I've always been told by Prae to increase the
number of members. Until now, I was also told to
focus on raising our reputation...

\nw[Taro]Even though we were half-asleep, we managed to
defeat the Earth Beast. As a mercenary group, we
should have become quite famous.
\nw[Nonna]That's true.

\nw[Taro]Because of that, we've started receiving requests
that require more members. But in the current
situation, we have no choice but to either seek
cooperation from other mercenary groups or
decline. That's why I want to increase our numbers
as soon as possible.

\nw[Nonna]It doesn't feel like we're actively recruiting,
considering that.

\nw[Taro]Well, considering the balance with the sex
workers, I want to increase the number of women
first.

\nw[Taro]Besides, there's also the possibility of becoming
succubi and NTR, so it's better to have young
mercenaries...

\nw[Taro]I want to increase the numbers as soon as possible
considering the current situation, but I'm afraid
of the problems that might arise from rushing, so
I've decided to choose carefully.

\nw[Nonna]I see, understood. If you're in trouble, let me
know. If there's anything I can do, I'll help you.
\nw[Taro]Ah, I'll rely on you at that time.

\nw[Taro]I plan to finish repaying my debt soon and quit

\nw[Fross]I will focus on my job as a healer. I couldn't do

\nw[Fross]I've also been going to the church less

\nw[Fross]Oh, if it's a job at a brothel, I can help. If

\nw[Fross]We were intimate every night until I was

\nw[Fross]I was feeling down and shocked, but at that time,

\nw[Fross]I fell in love with Rodrigo-san's incredible

\nw[Taro]Well, I guess that's true...

\nw[Taro](Well, I wonder if I was attracted to Rodrigo

\nw[Taro]Why did Fross decide to become a therapist?
\nw[Fross]Because I wanted to heal people who were hurt.

\nw[Fross]When I was a child, there was a war going on.
Because of that, there were many people suffering
from injuries and illnesses.

\nw[Fross]Even the people close to me are no exception.
That's why I decided to become a therapist.

\nw[Taro]I see... Unlike Dios, this country has been in a
state of war for a long time.

\nw[Fross]That's true, but after the king went mad, the
public order was also terrible. There was no
proper governance, you see.

\nw[Fross]There were soldiers who worked hard, but if the
top does nothing, there are limits to what can be
done.
\nw[Taro]I see...

\nw[Fross]The reason I'm here is because there are many
people fighting. The type of patients here is
different from those in a safe place.
\nw[Taro]You really made your dreams come true.
\nw[Fross]I'm not sure if you could call it a dream, though.

\nw[Fross]Are you not interested in the Amor religion?

\nw[Fross]In that case, would you like to come with me to

\nw[Shia]I do hope to catch up someday... but their back is
